VA two-day programme is being held on July 17 and 18 byArulamudhamspiritual magazine. Sri Satyanarayana homam and 108 vilakku puja were performed on July 17 and the Maha rudra homam is to be performed, under the guidance of 133 Ve\u000adic scholars, on July 18. The venue is Arulmigu Sri Selva Vinayakar Alayam, Nandi Nagar, Keelkattalai. For more details contact R.Parthasarathy, Arulamudham Publications, 31, Jawaharlal Nehru Road, Ekkaduthangal, Chennai &#8211; 600032. Phone: 94442 56421/3291 4548.
